                  <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;A <strong>Wizard</strong> is a Human class that deals mainly in magic. Unlike   other spell-casting classes, a Wizard's spells revolve around three   elements (fire, water, and earth), instead of just one. Wizards are all   about offense, and their weapons of choice are patakas, wands, glaives,   and magic swords. </p>